      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Several new delegates were seated\nIn the trades council last night They\nwere the following:\n\n\nw. Il. Emery of the brewerymen.\nGeorge Levison. II. j. Cunningham\nand Otto Bergman OF the cigarmak-\ners. Thomas joyce, d. r. Halstead.\nGeorge Munter and T. II. Taylor of\nthe bartenders, William Martin Of the\nplumbers, Miss Burrows OF the retail\nclerks, L. f. Mayhugh and Harry\nRitter Of the stablemen, w. A. Miller,\nIl. 9. Potts and e. Longale Of the\nbuilding laborers. C. s. Werner of the\nsheet metal workers. and @. II.\nKoonce. John J. Gratx and A. c.\nCrawford OF the butchers and drivers."
    }
